WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:26.522
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It scares us just thinking about it.</i></b></font>

2
00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:28.762
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>When you hear it. you're gonna
think we're insane.</i></b></font>

3
00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:31.611
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Try us. Please. from the start.</i></b></font>

4
00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:38.886
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It started out small. like a hand
or a leg was in a different position.</b></font>

5
00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:41.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then its head was looking up
instead of down.</b></font>

6
00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:44.769
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And then one day. it was in
a completely different room.</b></font>

7
00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:46.490
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was moving around by itself.</b></font>

8
00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:50.804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ever think maybe somebody had a key
to your apartment and was playing a trick?</b></font>

9
00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's exactly what we thought.</b></font>

10
00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.805
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But never once did we find any
sign or evidence of intrusion.</b></font>

11
00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:58.725
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And this all led you to believe
that the doll was possessed?</b></font>

12
00:00:58.880 --> 00:01:00.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

13
00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:04.161
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Camilla got in touch with a medium. We
learned from her that a 7-year-old girl...</b></font>

14
00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:07.244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...named Annabelle Higgins
had died in this apartment.</b></font>

15
00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:11.121
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She was lonely and took a liking
to my doll.</b></font>

16
00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:13.643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All she wanted was to be friends.</b></font>

17
00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:16.167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When we heard this.
we felt really sorry for her.</b></font>

18
00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:19.011
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I mean. we're nurses. we help people.</b></font>

19
00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.486
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So...</b></font>

20
00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:24.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...we gave her permission
to move into the doll.</b></font>

21
00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:26.282
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wait. you did what?</b></font>

22
00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.081
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She wanted to live with us
by inhabiting the doll.</b></font>

23
00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:30.446
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We said yes.</b></font>

24
00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:33.001
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But then things got worse.</b></font>

25
00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:48.371
<font color="#ffff00"><b>God.</b></font>

26
00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:54.363
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>When we came home.
she was sitting in the hallway.</i></b></font>

27
00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:56.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But we had left her
in the spare room.</i></b></font>

28
00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:36.962
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Debbie! Debbie. wait!</b></font>

29
00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:53.768
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We are beyond terrified.</b></font>

30
00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:57.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We don't know what's going on
or what to do. Can you help us?</b></font>

31
00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.525
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. we can.</b></font>

32
00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:05.010
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now. firstly. there's no such thing
as Annabelle. and there never was.</b></font>

33
00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:07.242
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ghosts don't possess such power.</b></font>

34
00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:10.051
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think what we have here is something
extremely manipulative.</b></font>

35
00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:12.168
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's something inhuman.</b></font>

36
00:04:12.600 --> 00:04:14.841
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was a big mistake
acknowledging this doll.</b></font>

37
00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:17.162
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And through that.
the inhuman spirit tricked you.</b></font>

38
00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:20.091
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You gave it permission
to infest your lives.</b></font>

39
00:04:20.600 --> 00:04:22.489
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's an inhuman spirit?</b></font>

40
00:04:23.080 --> 00:04:26.527
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's something that's never walked
the earth in human form.</b></font>

41
00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:28.809
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's something demonic.</b></font>

42
00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:34.768
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So the doll was never possessed?</b></font>

43
00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:36.849
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. no. it was used as a conduit.</b></font>

44
00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:39.361
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was moved around to give
the impression of possession.</b></font>

45
00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:43.206
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Demonic spirits don't possess things.
they possess people.</b></font>

46
00:04:44.280 --> 00:04:46.442
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It wanted to get inside of you.</b></font>

47
00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:59.202
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. that's good. Drew.
You can shut it down now.</b></font>

48
00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:02.041
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hit the lights.</b></font>

49
00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.168
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So we got the church to
send a priest over...</b></font>

50
00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.402
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...to bless the house and the occupants.</b></font>

51
00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:13.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Whatever was oppressing that apartment
was no longer with them. Any questions?</b></font>

52
00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.407
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

53
00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:18.210
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where's the doll now?</b></font>

54
00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Someplace safe.</b></font>

55
00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:23.562
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yep.
- So. what are you guys?</b></font>

56
00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:25.569
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I mean. what do people call you?</b></font>

57
00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:31.490
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Uh. well. we've been called Demonologists.
That's one name for us.</b></font>

58
00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ghost hunters. paranormal researchers.</b></font>

59
00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.847
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kooks.</b></font>

60
00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.445
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Wackos.</i></b></font>

61
00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:41.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But we prefer to be known simply
as Ed and Lorraine Warren.</b></font>

62
00:06:42.320 --> 00:06:43.845
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here we are.</b></font>

63
00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:49.448
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wow. hear that?</b></font>

64
00:06:49.600 --> 00:06:51.250
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I don't hear anything.
- Exactly.</b></font>

65
00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:52.640
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. Ha!</b></font>

66
00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:56.088
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Okay. Guys. we are here!
- Get out of the car.</b></font>

67
00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:58.129
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. God.
we're in the middle of nowhere.</b></font>

68
00:06:58.280 --> 00:07:01.329
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you so excited?
Where's my "yes"? Where's my "yes"?</b></font>

69
00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:02.601
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll race you!</b></font>

70
00:07:02.760 --> 00:07:05.001
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Are you guys excited?
- Yes!</b></font>

71
00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:07.168
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I'm so excited!
- Come on. Sadie!</b></font>

72
00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.850
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I get my own room!</b></font>

73
00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:11.685
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you kidding me?
No dibs on the rooms!</b></font>

74
00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:12.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What?
- What?</b></font>

75
00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:16.846
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So do I get to pick my own room?
Or do I have no choice in that either?</b></font>

76
00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:22.682
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. first cute boy she meets.
she'll forget about Jersey.</b></font>

77
00:07:22.840 --> 00:07:24.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Great.
- I hope.</b></font>

78
00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:25.486
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't wait.</b></font>

79
00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.360
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. Sadie.</b></font>

80
00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:29.885
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sadie. let's go.</b></font>

81
00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:32.484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. come.</b></font>

82
00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:35.210
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's the matter with you?</b></font>

83
00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:37.124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. come on. girl.</b></font>

84
00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. suit yourself.</b></font>

85
00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:54.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Watch your step.</b></font>

86
00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:55.845
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Coming through.</b></font>

87
00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:57.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Whoa. watch out. Dad.</b></font>

88
00:07:57.880 --> 00:07:59.760
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Where do you want it?
- In the living room.</b></font>

89
00:07:59.880 --> 00:08:02.880
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Andrea. where's my wind chime?
- I think Nancy's got it in the other room.</b></font>

90
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:05.241
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thanks. Hey. Nancy.
have you seen my wind chime?</b></font>

91
00:08:05.400 --> 00:08:07.050
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Oh. this one?
- Yeah. thanks.</b></font>

92
00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:10.044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- You're gonna have to catch it.
- Nancy! Let go! Give it here.</b></font>

93
00:08:10.520 --> 00:08:12.090
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so mean.</b></font>

94
00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:14.844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. Mom. can I hang up
my wind chime?</b></font>

95
00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.401
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course. There's a line outside
you can hang it on.</b></font>

96
00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:20.251
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Honey. have April come in. okay?
It's gonna be dark soon.</b></font>

97
00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:21.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

98
00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:33.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. April! Mom wants us inside!</b></font>

99
00:08:34.520 --> 00:08:36.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look what I found. Cindy.</b></font>

100
00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:57.725
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>One...</i></b></font>

101
00:08:58.240 --> 00:08:59.287
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...two...</b></font>

102
00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:00.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...three.</b></font>

103
00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.609
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. come on. come on.
No peeking.</b></font>

104
00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:04.125
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Four.</i></b></font>

105
00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:07.449
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you guys done with the pizza?
I don't want it going to waste.</b></font>

106
00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:10.046
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Let's go.
- It's expensive feeding you girls.</b></font>

107
00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:13.602
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Seven. eight. nine. ten.</b></font>

108
00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:14.921
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where should I hide?</b></font>

109
00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:17.282
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ready or not. here I come!</b></font>

110
00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:20.040
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. clap.</b></font>

111
00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.608
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Whoa!
- You don't know the house well enough.</b></font>

112
00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:31.841
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Someone's gonna get hurt.</b></font>

113
00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.286
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm okay. I'm okay.</b></font>

114
00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:36.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Second clap.</b></font>

115
00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:44.091
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's cheating.</b></font>

116
00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:57.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Clap.</b></font>

117
00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:01.885
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Got You!
- Aah!</b></font>

118
00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:04.528
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Are you okay? Um...
- Yeah.</b></font>

119
00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:06.565
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. what did we break now?</b></font>

120
00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:08.722
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I didn't mean to.
- Move out of there. please.</b></font>

121
00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was Christine's fault.</b></font>

122
00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.041
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Oh. jeez.
- My fault? Oh. my God.</b></font>

123
00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:15.123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Christine did it.
- No. I didn't.</b></font>

124
00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:17.442
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- You pushed me.
- No. no. you fell back.</b></font>

125
00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.285
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. Nancy. can you go get me
the matches. please?</b></font>

126
00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.326
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

127
00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:24.482
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Nancy broke something.
- Shut up.</b></font>

128
00:10:24.680 --> 00:10:26.523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What broke?
- It's the Wall.</b></font>

129
00:10:26.680 --> 00:10:29.729
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Whoa.
- I think we have a cellar or something.</b></font>

130
00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:33.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wanna see. I wanna see.
Move. move. move.</b></font>

131
00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:36.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here. matches. Thank you.</b></font>

132
00:10:37.160 --> 00:10:38.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I wanna see.
- You can see.</b></font>

133
00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:40.684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I wanna see.
- You can all see.</b></font>

134
00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.046
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Move!</b></font>

135
00:10:52.240 --> 00:10:54.083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. man.</b></font>

136
00:10:58.840 --> 00:10:59.887
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huh.</b></font>

137
00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:02.920
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Roger?</b></font>

138
00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.366
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you see down there?</b></font>

139
00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:09.050
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just. uh. hard to tell. you know?</b></font>

140
00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:13.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's an old piano
and a whole bunch of garbage.</b></font>

141
00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:17.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Agh. Son of a...</b></font>

142
00:11:21.280 --> 00:11:22.964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wow.</b></font>

143
00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:28.245
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Rog?</b></font>

144
00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.011
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on up.</b></font>

145
00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:37.969
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want you girls going down there.</b></font>

146
00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:39.849
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- That place is loaded with spiders.
- Ew!</b></font>

147
00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:41.087
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just relax. Okay.</b></font>

148
00:11:41.240 --> 00:11:43.561
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop it. Nancy. It's not funny.</b></font>

149
00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:47.442
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We've got extra square footage anyway.
I'll check it out in the morning.</b></font>

150
00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:49.802
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I wonder why it was boarded up.
- I don't know.</b></font>

151
00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:51.007
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. show's over.</b></font>

152
00:11:51.160 --> 00:11:52.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Five minutes.
- No more minutes.</b></font>

153
00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:55.407
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Up to bed. Please. Thank you.
- Right to bed.</b></font>

154
00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Man. I'm fried.</b></font>

155
00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:03.484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Something's up with Sadie.</b></font>

156
00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:07.601
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. I don't know what her problem is.
Couldn't get her to come inside.</b></font>

157
00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:09.564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We can't leave her out there.</b></font>

158
00:12:09.720 --> 00:12:11.882
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's all right. I got her on a chain.</b></font>

159
00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:15.970
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sadie. hey. be quiet.</b></font>

160
00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:20.962
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thanks for making this work.</b></font>

161
00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:23.009
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know it was a lot to bite off.</b></font>

162
00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:26.320
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's gonna be great. isn't it?</b></font>

163
00:12:26.920 --> 00:12:28.763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think it's great already.</b></font>

164
00:12:30.040 --> 00:12:31.121
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

165
00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:36.004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You still too fried to christen
the new house?</b></font>

166
00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:38.450
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who said I'm fried?</b></font>

167
00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:42.004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Ain't nobody here's fried.
- Ha. ha.</b></font>

168
00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.600
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mom?</b></font>

169
00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:21.207
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. How did you guys sleep?</b></font>

170
00:13:21.400 --> 00:13:22.561
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm cold.</b></font>

171
00:13:22.720 --> 00:13:24.245
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It is chilly. isn't it?</b></font>

172
00:13:24.560 --> 00:13:28.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You think maybe we could have bought
a house with a toilet that actually works?</b></font>

173
00:13:28.400 --> 00:13:29.447
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tell your father.</b></font>

174
00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:32.729
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And there was a funky smell in my
room last night. Like something died.</b></font>

175
00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:34.484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Is it still there?
- No.</b></font>

176
00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:35.687
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Problem solved.</b></font>

177
00:14:01.400 --> 00:14:02.561
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Roger?</b></font>

178
00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:05.531
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Roger?</b></font>

179
00:14:05.920 --> 00:14:07.445
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Down here. honey.</b></font>

180
00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:13.647
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Morning.</b></font>

181
00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:17.887
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ooh. Whoa.</b></font>

182
00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:20.731
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is gonna take some
serious elbow grease.</b></font>

183
00:14:20.920 --> 00:14:22.081
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

184
00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:24.884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. my God.</b></font>

185
00:14:31.800 --> 00:14:33.643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are we gonna do
with all this stuff?</b></font>

186
00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:36.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. we probably ought
to go through it. you know?</b></font>

187
00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:38.801
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There might be some antiques down here
worth a lot.</b></font>

188
00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:41.645
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. or just a lot of junk
the previous owner didn't want.</b></font>

189
00:14:42.080 --> 00:14:44.128
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- It's ours now.
- Knock yourself out.</b></font>

190
00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:46.768
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I'm gonna make some coffee.
- Okay.</b></font>

191
00:14:46.920 --> 00:14:48.968
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm gonna see if I can get
this furnace working.</b></font>

192
00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:50.929
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. that'd be nice. It's freezing.</b></font>

193
00:14:51.080 --> 00:14:52.241
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

194
00:15:01.280 --> 00:15:02.884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hmm.</b></font>

195
00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:08.045
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sadie! Come here. Sadie!</b></font>

196
00:15:08.360 --> 00:15:09.646
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mommy!</b></font>

197
00:15:10.840 --> 00:15:12.285
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mommy. where's Sadie?</b></font>

198
00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:16.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's outside. I'm sure she's hungry by now.
Why don't you go and get her.</b></font>

199
00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:18.807
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Whoa.
- Morning. Dad.</b></font>

200
00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:20.962
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Can you hold this?
- Sure.</b></font>

201
00:15:21.120 --> 00:15:22.804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sadie!
Slow it down. Scoot.</b></font>

202
00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:24.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Roger.
- Yeah.</b></font>

203
00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:27.569
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This clock stopped at 3:07.
and so did the one in the hallway.</b></font>

204
00:15:27.720 --> 00:15:29.131
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's weird.</b></font>

205
00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:32.809
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe it got knocked around in the move.</b></font>

206
00:15:32.960 --> 00:15:35.850
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Speaking of knocked around.
what did you do to me last night?</b></font>

207
00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:38.765
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Ouch. I didn't do that. Did I?
- I don't know.</b></font>

208
00:15:38.920 --> 00:15:41.366
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sadie!</b></font>

209
00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:53.367
<font color="#ffff00"><b>April! April!</b></font>

210
00:15:53.520 --> 00:15:56.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's...? April! What's going on?</b></font>

211
00:15:56.280 --> 00:15:58.601
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What happened?
- Oh. my God!</b></font>

212
00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:00.411
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. Sadie.</b></font>

213
00:16:10.520 --> 00:16:12.568
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We keep everything locked in here.</b></font>

214
00:16:13.000 --> 00:16:14.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Feel free to look around.</b></font>

215
00:16:15.200 --> 00:16:16.804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just don't touch anything.</b></font>

216
00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:20.770
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wow.</b></font>

217
00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:23.530
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is crazy.</b></font>

218
00:16:25.520 --> 00:16:28.444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So all these are taken from cases
you've investigated?</b></font>

219
00:16:28.600 --> 00:16:32.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right. Everything you see
in here is either haunted. cursed...</b></font>

220
00:16:32.760 --> 00:16:35.684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...or has been used in some kind
of ritualistic practice.</b></font>

221
00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:38.004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nothing's a toy.</b></font>

222
00:16:38.160 --> 00:16:39.844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not even the toy monkey.</b></font>

223
00:16:41.280 --> 00:16:42.725
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't touch it.</b></font>

224
00:16:44.920 --> 00:16:49.403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. ahem. Well. isn't it scary.
or doesn't it worry you...</b></font>

225
00:16:49.560 --> 00:16:51.847
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...to have all these items
right in your home?</b></font>

226
00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:55.402
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's why we have a priest that comes by
once a month to bless the room.</b></font>

227
00:16:55.560 --> 00:16:56.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. the way I see it is:</b></font>

228
00:16:56.920 --> 00:16:59.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's safer for these things
to be in here than out there.</b></font>

229
00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:01.529
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's kind of like keeping guns
off the street.</b></font>

230
00:17:01.680 --> 00:17:04.763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why not just throw them
in an incinerator? Destroy them.</b></font>

231
00:17:04.960 --> 00:17:06.849
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. that would only destroy the vessel.</b></font>

232
00:17:07.360 --> 00:17:10.170
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sometimes it's better to keep
the genie in the bottle.</b></font>

233
00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:14.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Say. is the. uh. Annabelle doll here?</b></font>

234
00:17:16.120 --> 00:17:17.485
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right this way.</b></font>

235
00:17:19.800 --> 00:17:21.086
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

236
00:17:29.880 --> 00:17:32.326
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- You said she's a conduit?
- That's right.</b></font>

237
00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What does that mean?</b></font>

238
00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:37.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A very powerful demonic
has latched itself onto her.</b></font>

239
00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:40.810
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So when you guys investigate
these hauntings...</b></font>

240
00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:43.201
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...how do you stop them
from latching onto you?</b></font>

241
00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:44.930
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have to take great precaution.</b></font>

242
00:17:45.120 --> 00:17:46.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But what about your wife?</b></font>

243
00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:48.965
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What about her?</b></font>

244
00:17:50.080 --> 00:17:51.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. Father Gordon told me that...</b></font>

245
00:17:52.040 --> 00:17:53.530
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. that was different.</b></font>

246
00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:56.890
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What happened to my wife
happened during an exorcism.</b></font>

247
00:17:57.040 --> 00:17:58.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. what's the difference?</b></font>

248
00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:01.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Excuse me.</b></font>

249
00:18:03.560 --> 00:18:04.800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Honey. what are you doing?</b></font>

250
00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:06.401
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come here.</b></font>

251
00:18:06.600 --> 00:18:08.921
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know better. All right?</b></font>

252
00:18:09.080 --> 00:18:10.525
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Georgiana?</b></font>

253
00:18:10.800 --> 00:18:13.087
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Come on. Did you touch anything?
- No.</b></font>

254
00:18:13.240 --> 00:18:14.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. come on. honey.</b></font>

255
00:18:15.400 --> 00:18:17.971
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Georgiana! Could you take Judy upstairs?
- Oh. sure.</b></font>

256
00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:20.600
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You can't go into this room.
no matter what. remember?</b></font>

257
00:18:20.760 --> 00:18:22.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yes. Daddy.
- All right.</b></font>

258
00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:24.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Go on.
- Okay. come on.</b></font>

259
00:18:24.440 --> 00:18:27.489
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's see if I can find you
a little snack. okay? Come on.</b></font>

260
00:18:35.720 --> 00:18:37.802
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. What's going on in here?</b></font>

261
00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:40.440
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Daddy. look.
- You look very pretty.</b></font>

262
00:18:40.600 --> 00:18:42.967
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. all done.
Go get dressed for dinner.</b></font>

263
00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:45.964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I'm wearing it to dinner.
- No. you're not!</b></font>

264
00:18:47.080 --> 00:18:48.366
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here you go.</b></font>

265
00:18:49.120 --> 00:18:50.451
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How'd it go?</b></font>

266
00:18:50.600 --> 00:18:52.728
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. I think he may write
a positive article.</b></font>

267
00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ooh. a non-skeptic.</b></font>

268
00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:56.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's a pleasant change.</b></font>

269
00:18:56.840 --> 00:18:58.001
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

270
00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:06.644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop blaming yourself.</b></font>

271
00:19:17.600 --> 00:19:19.045
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No sugar.</b></font>

272
00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:21.685
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Be right back.</b></font>

273
00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:19.448
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not funny. Nancy.</b></font>

274
00:20:20.600 --> 00:20:21.840
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

275
00:20:22.640 --> 00:20:24.608
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop grabbing my foot.</b></font>

276
00:20:24.800 --> 00:20:26.928
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shut up. I didn't do anything.</b></font>

277
00:20:27.760 --> 00:20:29.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. right.</b></font>

278
00:20:30.920 --> 00:20:32.888
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And stop farting.</b></font>

279
00:20:33.320 --> 00:20:35.129
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It really stinks.</b></font>

280
00:20:35.560 --> 00:20:39.042
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't blame that on me. It's you. Pew.</b></font>

281
00:22:55.320 --> 00:22:56.401
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dad?</b></font>

282
00:22:56.600 --> 00:22:58.602
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Andrea. what are you doing out of bed?</b></font>

283
00:22:58.840 --> 00:23:00.046
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's that sound?</b></font>

284
00:23:00.200 --> 00:23:04.125
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's Cindy. She's in my room.
She's sleepwalking again.</b></font>

285
00:23:19.560 --> 00:23:21.688
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've never seen her do this before.</b></font>

286
00:23:25.840 --> 00:23:28.241
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I remembered you saying not
to wake her if she's like this.</b></font>

287
00:23:28.400 --> 00:23:30.323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. we just put her back to bed.</b></font>

288
00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:33.006
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. hey. Sweetie. Shh.</b></font>

289
00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:35.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's go back to bed.</b></font>

290
00:23:46.360 --> 00:23:47.964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's okay. Good night.</b></font>

291
00:23:48.120 --> 00:23:49.326
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Night.</b></font>

292
00:24:02.320 --> 00:24:05.449
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>She's sleepwalking again?
She hasn't done that for awhile.</i></b></font>

293
00:24:06.120 --> 00:24:09.203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She ended up in Andrea's room too.
I think kind of freaked her out.</b></font>

294
00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:11.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- That's not good. What are we gonna do?
- I don't know.</b></font>

295
00:24:12.120 --> 00:24:14.691
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Honey. you got another bruise here.
- Hmm?</b></font>

296
00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:16.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Does that hurt?</b></font>

297
00:24:18.240 --> 00:24:19.366
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's weird.</b></font>

298
00:24:19.560 --> 00:24:22.484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't know. Will you do me a favor.
go see a doctor for that?</b></font>

299
00:24:23.320 --> 00:24:25.607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yeah. I will. Drive safe.
- Yeah.</b></font>

300
00:24:25.760 --> 00:24:27.489
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I love you.
- I love you too.</b></font>

301
00:24:57.960 --> 00:24:59.086
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Bye!</b></font>

302
00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:00.730
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Love you!</b></font>

303
00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:04.770
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Cindy. you have your lunch?
- Yeah.</b></font>

304
00:25:06.320 --> 00:25:08.402
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. I do.</b></font>

305
00:25:08.560 --> 00:25:10.403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I miss Sadie a lot.</b></font>

306
00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:12.927
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She was my best friend.</b></font>

307
00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:16.009
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're my friend. right?</b></font>

308
00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:19.250
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. let's play.</b></font>

309
00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:28.125
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Who are you talking to?
- Rory.</b></font>

310
00:25:28.520 --> 00:25:29.681
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Rory?</b></font>

311
00:25:30.080 --> 00:25:32.082
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- He's my new friend.
- Oh. really?</b></font>

312
00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:35.323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yeah. do you want to see him?
- Yeah. Uh-huh. How?</b></font>

313
00:25:35.480 --> 00:25:36.925
<font color="#ffff00"><b>With this.</b></font>

314
00:25:37.080 --> 00:25:40.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When the music stops. you see him
in the mirror standing behind you.</b></font>

315
00:25:41.640 --> 00:25:42.801
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

316
00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:44.883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But you have to twist the key.</b></font>

317
00:25:45.040 --> 00:25:46.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

318
00:26:09.920 --> 00:26:11.410
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Boo. Mommy! Ha-ha!
- Oh!</b></font>

319
00:26:11.920 --> 00:26:14.890
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- April. you just gave me a heart attack.
- Got you!</b></font>

320
00:26:15.840 --> 00:26:18.923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. okay. I guess Rory
doesn't want to see me. huh?</b></font>

321
00:26:19.080 --> 00:26:20.320
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hmm. Oh. well.</b></font>

322
00:26:20.560 --> 00:26:22.164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can we play hide and clap?</b></font>

323
00:26:22.320 --> 00:26:24.607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hide and cla...?
Oh. honey. I don't want to play.</b></font>

324
00:26:24.760 --> 00:26:28.367
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Please! Nobody ever lets me play.
- Okay. okay.</b></font>

325
00:26:30.040 --> 00:26:33.328
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Remember. you get to ask me
for three claps.</b></font>

326
00:26:33.480 --> 00:26:34.527
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

327
00:26:34.680 --> 00:26:37.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One. two. three.</b></font>

328
00:26:38.040 --> 00:26:39.690
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I'm gonna go hide now!
- Okay.</b></font>

329
00:26:39.840 --> 00:26:42.525
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Four. five...</b></font>

330
00:26:42.680 --> 00:26:45.570
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...six. seven...</b></font>

331
00:26:45.720 --> 00:26:48.087
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...eight. nine...</b></font>

332
00:26:48.680 --> 00:26:49.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...ten!</b></font>

333
00:26:52.640 --> 00:26:54.165
<font color="#ffff00"><b>First clap!</b></font>

334
00:27:13.680 --> 00:27:15.489
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ow. Shit.</b></font>

335
00:27:15.640 --> 00:27:17.165
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Second clap!</b></font>

336
00:27:32.680 --> 00:27:35.047
<font color="#ffff00"><b>April.</b></font>

337
00:27:40.920 --> 00:27:42.445
<font color="#ffff00"><b>April.</b></font>

338
00:27:53.000 --> 00:27:55.685
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. I know where you're hiding.</b></font>

339
00:27:55.880 --> 00:27:57.962
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Give me the third clap.</b></font>

340
00:28:06.520 --> 00:28:07.965
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm gonna get you now.</b></font>

341
00:28:15.320 --> 00:28:17.049
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can hear you breathing.</b></font>

342
00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:19.051
<font color="#ffff00"><b>April.</b></font>

343
00:28:20.040 --> 00:28:21.451
<font color="#ffff00"><b>April.</b></font>

344
00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:30.447
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ha. ha. You took your blindfold off. I win!</b></font>

345
00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:34.486
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You weren't even warm. Mom.
I was in Christine and Nancy's room.</b></font>

346
00:28:38.960 --> 00:28:42.806
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I gotta have some routes here.
or I'm gonna lose the insurance on the rig.</i></b></font>

347
00:28:44.840 --> 00:28:47.491
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's like half of my rate. man.</b></font>

348
00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:51.162
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. okay.</b></font>

349
00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:54.242
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll. uh... Yeah. I'll take it.</b></font>

350
00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:55.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

351
00:28:58.400 --> 00:29:01.370
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What's the route?
- It's. uh. Florida.</b></font>

352
00:29:01.520 --> 00:29:04.251
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's a week turnaround. I start tomorrow.</b></font>

353
00:29:05.040 --> 00:29:06.565
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We'll get through this.</b></font>

354
00:29:08.480 --> 00:29:09.606
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

355
00:29:09.760 --> 00:29:11.091
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. let's go to bed.</b></font>

356
00:29:35.480 --> 00:29:39.007
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop it. Nancy. It's not funny anymore.</b></font>

357
00:29:39.160 --> 00:29:42.243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm trying to sleep.
please stop grabbing my feet.</b></font>

358
00:31:26.600 --> 00:31:28.045
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy?</b></font>

359
00:31:30.040 --> 00:31:31.610
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy?</b></font>

360
00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:35.729
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

361
00:31:39.320 --> 00:31:40.651
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Christine?</b></font>

362
00:31:42.360 --> 00:31:43.441
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you all right?</b></font>

363
00:31:45.360 --> 00:31:46.771
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you see it?</b></font>

364
00:31:49.560 --> 00:31:50.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>See what?</b></font>

365
00:31:56.240 --> 00:31:58.322
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's someone behind the door.</b></font>

366
00:31:58.480 --> 00:31:59.720
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

367
00:32:02.200 --> 00:32:04.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's someone standing over there.</b></font>

368
00:32:07.200 --> 00:32:09.407
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't see anyone.</b></font>

369
00:32:11.840 --> 00:32:14.161
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's looking right at us.</b></font>

370
00:32:23.520 --> 00:32:24.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy. don't! Nancy.</b></font>

371
00:32:25.080 --> 00:32:27.526
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. no. Look. Look.</b></font>

372
00:32:27.680 --> 00:32:31.162
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look. there's no one here. See?</b></font>

373
00:32:32.040 --> 00:32:34.805
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ugh. It's that smell again.</b></font>

374
00:32:35.120 --> 00:32:37.282
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. my God.</b></font>

375
00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:40.924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's standing right behind you.</b></font>

376
00:32:56.720 --> 00:32:59.929
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Christine?! Christine! Christine!</b></font>

377
00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:02.450
<font color="#ffff00"><b>God. it won't op...</b></font>

378
00:33:03.800 --> 00:33:05.723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Christine!
- No! No! No!</b></font>

379
00:33:05.920 --> 00:33:08.924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What's going on? What happened?
- There was someone else in here!</b></font>

380
00:33:09.080 --> 00:33:10.127
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What? Where?</b></font>

381
00:33:10.280 --> 00:33:13.568
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the door. It was behind the door.</b></font>

382
00:33:13.760 --> 00:33:16.286
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Honey. there's nothing in here.
There's nobody in here.</b></font>

383
00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:18.249
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There was someone else in here!</b></font>

384
00:33:18.400 --> 00:33:22.849
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was just sleeping. and then
I felt somebody grab my feet.</b></font>

385
00:33:23.000 --> 00:33:25.321
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I thought it was Nancy.</b></font>

386
00:33:25.520 --> 00:33:28.808
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. honey. I'm pretty sure
that it was just a bad dream.</b></font>

387
00:33:28.960 --> 00:33:31.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No! It talked to me!</b></font>

388
00:33:31.840 --> 00:33:33.649
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It said...</b></font>

389
00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:37.881
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...that it wants my family dead.</b></font>

390
00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:47.400
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mr. Winston!</b></font>

391
00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:49.564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Winston? Winston?</b></font>

392
00:33:49.920 --> 00:33:51.331
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get behind him.</b></font>

393
00:33:52.120 --> 00:33:53.167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where you off to?</b></font>

394
00:33:53.320 --> 00:33:55.800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just gotta run to the store
for a few things.</b></font>

395
00:33:57.160 --> 00:33:59.970
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Why do you even try?
- What? What do you mean?</b></font>

396
00:34:00.120 --> 00:34:02.691
<font color="#ffff00"><b>In 15 years have you
ever been able to lie to me?</b></font>

397
00:34:03.920 --> 00:34:06.810
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Father Gordon called. He's got
a case he wants us to look into.</b></font>

398
00:34:06.960 --> 00:34:09.531
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I said I'd go check it out myself.
Lorraine. myself.</b></font>

399
00:34:09.680 --> 00:34:11.045
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm going with you.</b></font>

400
00:34:11.960 --> 00:34:14.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know you're worried
it's gonna happen again.</b></font>

401
00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:16.249
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. I am. I really am.</b></font>

402
00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:23.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe it's just time we take a break.
Write that book.</b></font>

403
00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:27.965
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you remember what you said to me
on our wedding night?</b></font>

404
00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:29.970
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"Can we do it again?"</b></font>

405
00:34:32.840 --> 00:34:34.001
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After that.</b></font>

406
00:34:36.440 --> 00:34:40.240
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You said that God brought us together
for a reason. Right?</b></font>

407
00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:43.370
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm pretty sure it's not to write a book.</b></font>

408
00:34:46.040 --> 00:34:47.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm gonna get dressed.</b></font>

409
00:34:51.160 --> 00:34:53.367
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>We've isolated the
disturbances to the attic.</i></b></font>

410
00:34:53.520 --> 00:34:54.881
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I want you to listen for a second.</i></b></font>

411
00:34:56.200 --> 00:34:57.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. my God. that's it.</b></font>

412
00:34:58.920 --> 00:35:00.365
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do it again. Ed.</b></font>

413
00:35:02.240 --> 00:35:05.562
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right now it's just my weight. But you
take the water coming off the pipe...</b></font>

414
00:35:05.720 --> 00:35:08.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...combined with the wind coming
through the broken window...</b></font>

415
00:35:08.440 --> 00:35:10.800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...these boards are gonna expand
and rub against each other.</b></font>

416
00:35:10.960 --> 00:35:14.726
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You heard it all through the house because
of these pipes leading to the radiator.</b></font>

417
00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:16.843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So this place isn't haunted?</b></font>

418
00:35:17.000 --> 00:35:18.604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. it rarely is.</b></font>

419
00:35:18.800 --> 00:35:22.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. there's usually always
some kind of rational explanation.</b></font>

420
00:36:04.880 --> 00:36:07.451
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Girls. it's way past your bedtime.</b></font>

421
00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:06.050
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who is that?</b></font>

422
00:39:08.440 --> 00:39:11.011
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who's ever down there.
I'm gonna lock you in now!</b></font>

423
00:39:11.680 --> 00:39:12.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aah! Uhh.</b></font>

424
00:40:02.320 --> 00:40:03.810
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aah!</b></font>

425
00:40:04.920 --> 00:40:06.445
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Help!</b></font>

426
00:40:06.600 --> 00:40:08.409
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Andrea! Help!</b></font>

427
00:40:33.080 --> 00:40:35.526
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Hey. wanna play hide-and-clap?</i></b></font>

428
00:40:38.680 --> 00:40:40.364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aah!</b></font>

429
00:41:10.160 --> 00:41:11.400
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy?</b></font>

430
00:41:26.200 --> 00:41:28.043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. now...</b></font>

431
00:41:29.280 --> 00:41:30.520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right?</b></font>

432
00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:32.285
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. come on.</b></font>

433
00:41:32.640 --> 00:41:33.880
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on.</b></font>

434
00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:36.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There you go.</b></font>

435
00:41:36.720 --> 00:41:40.088
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. you can just sleep with me tonight.
all right?</b></font>

436
00:41:44.960 --> 00:41:46.325
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There you go.</b></font>

437
00:41:47.720 --> 00:41:48.881
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There.</b></font>

438
00:42:52.520 --> 00:42:54.966
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Andrea?
- Help! Help! Help!</b></font>

439
00:42:57.160 --> 00:42:58.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Who's in here?
- Andrea!</b></font>

440
00:42:58.920 --> 00:43:01.127
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Andrea? Andrea!</b></font>

441
00:43:01.280 --> 00:43:02.406
<font color="#ffff00"><b>In here!</b></font>

442
00:43:02.600 --> 00:43:05.046
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Help. Daddy! Help. it's Andrea!</b></font>

443
00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:06.645
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Who's in here?
- Andrea!</b></font>

444
00:43:07.120 --> 00:43:08.610
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>What happened?</i></b></font>

445
00:43:10.760 --> 00:43:13.206
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Somebody. goddamn it.
tell me what's going on here?</b></font>

446
00:43:17.400 --> 00:43:22.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Fear is defined as a feeling of agitation
and anxiety caused by the presence...</i></b></font>

447
00:43:22.440 --> 00:43:23.965
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>...or imminence of danger.</i></b></font>

448
00:43:24.160 --> 00:43:28.643
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Whether it's a ghost. a spirit
or an entity. they all feed on it.</i></b></font>

449
00:43:28.800 --> 00:43:29.847
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Take Maurice here.</b></font>

450
00:43:30.040 --> 00:43:33.203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A French-Canadian farmer with
no more than a third-grade education...</b></font>

451
00:43:33.360 --> 00:43:36.887
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...yet after he was possessed. spoke
some of the best Latin I'd ever heard.</b></font>

452
00:43:37.040 --> 00:43:38.280
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sometimes backwards.</b></font>

453
00:43:38.440 --> 00:43:42.161
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He'd been molested by his father.
who had also tortured him repeatedly.</b></font>

454
00:43:43.440 --> 00:43:45.807
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A dark spirit made its home in this man.</b></font>

455
00:43:45.960 --> 00:43:50.409
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now. if you look into his eyes.
you can see him tearing blood.</b></font>

456
00:43:57.960 --> 00:43:59.405
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And like that...</b></font>

457
00:43:59.560 --> 00:44:03.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...an upside-down cross started
to appear from within his body.</b></font>

458
00:44:06.600 --> 00:44:08.682
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Drew. you can hit the lights.</b></font>

459
00:44:09.160 --> 00:44:10.207
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh.</b></font>

460
00:44:10.360 --> 00:44:12.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you personally perform the exorcism?</b></font>

461
00:44:12.920 --> 00:44:15.730
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. I'm not authorized.
But I've assisted on many.</b></font>

462
00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:17.843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>See. an exorcism
can be very dangerous...</b></font>

463
00:44:18.000 --> 00:44:21.049
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...not only for the victim.
but for anyone in the room.</b></font>

464
00:44:21.720 --> 00:44:24.121
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What happened to Maurice?
- He tried to kill his wife...</b></font>

465
00:44:24.400 --> 00:44:27.643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...but instead shot her in the arm
and then turned the gun on himself.</b></font>

466
00:44:27.800 --> 00:44:31.247
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maurice had a very troubled life
with little to live for...</b></font>

467
00:44:31.400 --> 00:44:34.290
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...and not even an exorcist
could bring him back.</b></font>

468
00:44:34.840 --> 00:44:37.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Which brings us to the three stages
of demonic activity:</b></font>

469
00:44:38.040 --> 00:44:40.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Infestation. oppression and possession.</b></font>

470
00:44:40.440 --> 00:44:41.805
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now. infestation:</b></font>

471
00:44:41.960 --> 00:44:45.931
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's the whispering. the footsteps.
the feeling of another presence...</b></font>

472
00:44:46.120 --> 00:44:49.761
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...which ultimately grows
into oppression. the second stage.</b></font>

473
00:44:49.920 --> 00:44:52.207
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now this is where the victim.
and it's usually the one...</b></font>

474
00:44:52.360 --> 00:44:54.249
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...who's the most
psychologically vulnerable...</b></font>

475
00:44:54.400 --> 00:44:57.290
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...is targeted specifically
by an external force.</b></font>

476
00:44:57.440 --> 00:45:00.887
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Breaks the victim down.
Crushes their will.</b></font>

477
00:45:01.080 --> 00:45:06.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And. once in a weakened state. leads them
to the third and final stage: possession.</b></font>

478
00:45:09.440 --> 00:45:11.010
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Hey. Ed? Lorraine?
- Yeah.</b></font>

479
00:45:11.160 --> 00:45:13.606
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's someone here
that would like to talk to you.</b></font>

480
00:45:13.760 --> 00:45:14.807
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Hi.
- Thanks. Drew.</b></font>

481
00:45:14.960 --> 00:45:16.450
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Thank you.
- I'll see you later.</b></font>

482
00:45:16.600 --> 00:45:17.681
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can we help you?</b></font>

483
00:45:17.840 --> 00:45:22.164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's something horrible happening in
my house. Could you come and take a look?</b></font>

484
00:45:22.440 --> 00:45:24.283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know. uh. it's getting kinda late.</b></font>

485
00:45:24.440 --> 00:45:27.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- We really need to head to our family.
- You don't understand.</b></font>

486
00:45:27.360 --> 00:45:30.250
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But we do. There's usually some
sort of rational explanation...</b></font>

487
00:45:30.400 --> 00:45:35.167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have five daughters who are scared to death.
I'm so afraid this thing wants to hurt us.</b></font>

488
00:45:35.320 --> 00:45:39.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have a daughter. Wouldn't you do
anything you could to protect her? Please.</b></font>

489
00:45:39.320 --> 00:45:41.527
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please can you come and take a look?</b></font>

490
00:45:42.960 --> 00:45:44.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course we will.</b></font>

491
00:45:45.120 --> 00:45:46.610
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course we will.</b></font>

492
00:45:58.520 --> 00:46:00.682
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Come on. Jan! Open up!</i></b></font>

493
00:46:02.160 --> 00:46:03.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Jan. what happened?</i></b></font>

494
00:46:04.920 --> 00:46:06.524
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>The top of your head turned black.</i></b></font>

495
00:46:06.680 --> 00:46:08.444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You guys straighten up? Thanks.</b></font>

496
00:46:08.600 --> 00:46:10.409
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Don't be silly. it's a wig.</i></b></font>

497
00:46:14.360 --> 00:46:15.691
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Hello. Hi.
- Hi. Hi.</b></font>

498
00:46:15.840 --> 00:46:17.251
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thanks for coming.</b></font>

499
00:46:18.040 --> 00:46:19.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Hi. I'm Roger.
- Lorraine.</b></font>

500
00:46:19.920 --> 00:46:22.207
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. nice to meet you. Roger.
Ed Warren.</b></font>

501
00:46:22.840 --> 00:46:24.649
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Thanks for coming.
- Please. come in.</b></font>

502
00:46:24.840 --> 00:46:26.046
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

503
00:46:27.600 --> 00:46:28.681
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So...</b></font>

504
00:46:28.840 --> 00:46:31.844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. my God. Look at you all.
Who are these beautiful young women?</b></font>

505
00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:35.368
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is Andrea. the oldest.
Nancy. Cindy. Christine...</b></font>

506
00:46:35.560 --> 00:46:37.130
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...and April.</b></font>

507
00:46:38.840 --> 00:46:40.285
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's Mr. and Mrs. Warren.</b></font>

508
00:46:40.880 --> 00:46:43.565
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- We're all sleeping down here now.
- Mm.</b></font>

509
00:46:44.000 --> 00:46:46.765
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The girls feel safer and it's warmer.</b></font>

510
00:46:47.120 --> 00:46:50.647
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm constantly turning up the heat.
but the house is always freezing.</b></font>

511
00:46:50.800 --> 00:46:52.723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's not a problem with the furnace.</b></font>

512
00:46:52.880 --> 00:46:54.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I mean. not that I can find.</b></font>

513
00:46:59.400 --> 00:47:03.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's gotten a lot
worse the past few nights.</b></font>

514
00:47:03.680 --> 00:47:09.050
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's this awful smell. like rotting meat.
It moves around the house.</b></font>

515
00:47:12.000 --> 00:47:13.081
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Uh...</b></font>

516
00:47:13.240 --> 00:47:14.446
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What? What is it?</b></font>

517
00:47:15.160 --> 00:47:20.530
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. rancid smells could indicate
some type of demonic activity.</b></font>

518
00:47:20.760 --> 00:47:21.841
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. my God.</b></font>

519
00:47:26.280 --> 00:47:28.567
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's to keep those doors
from banging at night.</b></font>

520
00:47:28.720 --> 00:47:32.167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Otherwise. it's like:
All night long. just like that.</b></font>

521
00:47:33.520 --> 00:47:35.648
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Does it come in threes?
- Yeah.</b></font>

522
00:47:35.800 --> 00:47:36.961
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It stops at dawn?</b></font>

523
00:47:37.560 --> 00:47:38.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Uh-huh.</b></font>

524
00:47:40.760 --> 00:47:44.048
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. sometimes it's meant
as an insult to the Trinity:</b></font>

525
00:47:44.200 --> 00:47:46.168
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The Father. the Son and the Holy Spirit.</b></font>

526
00:47:47.880 --> 00:47:51.487
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know. it's the damndest thing.
but we also get all kinds of birds...</b></font>

527
00:47:51.680 --> 00:47:54.650
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...that will just fly against the side
of the house and break their necks.</b></font>

528
00:47:54.800 --> 00:47:56.450
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hm. Really?</b></font>

529
00:47:56.640 --> 00:47:59.041
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And the clocks stop at 3:07 a.m.</b></font>

530
00:47:59.200 --> 00:48:01.282
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- All of them?
- Every one.</b></font>

531
00:48:04.600 --> 00:48:07.444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. we were hanging those
along the stairs.</b></font>

532
00:48:07.600 --> 00:48:11.889
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Something just kept knocking them down.
so we stopped hanging them up.</b></font>

533
00:48:15.320 --> 00:48:17.607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's what I was talking about.</b></font>

534
00:48:17.920 --> 00:48:19.684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was here when we moved in.</b></font>

535
00:48:19.840 --> 00:48:22.047
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's also a lot of stuff in the cellar.</b></font>

536
00:48:25.120 --> 00:48:26.451
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Show me the cellar.</b></font>

537
00:48:38.560 --> 00:48:41.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Look what she made me do.</i></b></font>

538
00:48:41.400 --> 00:48:43.801
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You picking up anything in here. hon?</b></font>

539
00:48:47.520 --> 00:48:50.285
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Something awful happened here. Ed.</b></font>

540
00:48:54.080 --> 00:48:57.323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Those bruises. they from something
that happened here?</b></font>

