01:02:48.280 --> 01:02:49.520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wasn't me.</b></font>

716
01:03:04.040 --> 01:03:05.530
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Brad. get the camera.</b></font>

717
01:03:09.360 --> 01:03:10.441
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

718
01:03:16.720 --> 01:03:21.203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. it's 9:18. we're headed down into the
cellar where the door's just opened on its own.</b></font>

719
01:03:21.400 --> 01:03:24.210
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have Lorraine and Officer Brad Hamilton
with me.</b></font>

720
01:03:24.440 --> 01:03:26.568
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's keep the cellar light off.</b></font>

721
01:03:40.560 --> 01:03:43.404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Give us a sign that you wanna
communicate with us.</b></font>

722
01:04:11.920 --> 01:04:13.445
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hon. you all right?</b></font>

723
01:04:17.800 --> 01:04:20.246
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's definitely something here.</b></font>

724
01:04:21.640 --> 01:04:24.769
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- All right. close the door. Move something.
- My hands are so cold.</b></font>

725
01:04:27.120 --> 01:04:28.326
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on.</b></font>

726
01:04:33.480 --> 01:04:34.641
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

727
01:04:34.800 --> 01:04:36.450
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's gone. It's gone.</b></font>

728
01:04:36.640 --> 01:04:38.130
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I got nothing.</b></font>

729
01:04:38.440 --> 01:04:39.771
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

730
01:05:00.360 --> 01:05:03.807
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well. like I said. it doesn't
always work when you want it to.</b></font>

731
01:05:04.320 --> 01:05:06.766
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. maybe the camera picked
something up.</b></font>

732
01:05:07.560 --> 01:05:08.846
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Watch out!</b></font>

733
01:05:12.640 --> 01:05:14.165
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For a guy who doesn't believe...</b></font>

734
01:05:14.320 --> 01:05:17.688
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...you looked a little freaked out
when that door slammed shut.</b></font>

735
01:05:20.560 --> 01:05:22.608
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It must have been a draft.</b></font>

736
01:05:23.080 --> 01:05:24.809
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. that's funny.</b></font>

737
01:05:25.320 --> 01:05:27.926
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A draft never put that look
on my face before.</b></font>

738
01:05:30.600 --> 01:05:32.364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I believe the clock.</b></font>

739
01:05:34.000 --> 01:05:35.604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's 3208.</b></font>

740
01:05:45.800 --> 01:05:47.370
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me see your glasses.</b></font>

741
01:05:47.680 --> 01:05:48.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For you.</b></font>

742
01:05:48.920 --> 01:05:52.641
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think I might take some girls for ice cream later on.
What do you say about that?</b></font>

743
01:05:52.840 --> 01:05:55.002
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yeah!
- Honey. you wanna come?</b></font>

744
01:05:55.160 --> 01:05:58.209
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm exhausted. I'm just gonna take a nap.
The late nights are getting to me.</b></font>

745
01:05:58.360 --> 01:06:00.761
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's probably a good idea.
Why don't you get some rest.</b></font>

746
01:06:00.960 --> 01:06:03.566
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Lorraine and I'll watch over things for a bit.
- Really?</b></font>

747
01:06:03.720 --> 01:06:06.451
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm gonna take off.
I have a shift starting in an hour.</b></font>

748
01:06:06.600 --> 01:06:08.762
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The house hasn't felt like this
in a long time.</b></font>

749
01:06:08.960 --> 01:06:11.884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think the kids feel a lot safer
with you around.</b></font>

750
01:06:15.440 --> 01:06:17.886
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I could get used to this.
- What. me doing laundry?</b></font>

751
01:06:20.000 --> 01:06:21.843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Ha. ha. ha.
- You're funny.</b></font>

752
01:06:22.480 --> 01:06:24.005
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. this place.</b></font>

753
01:06:24.400 --> 01:06:26.482
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nice. fresh country air.</b></font>

754
01:06:30.280 --> 01:06:32.851
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They have such a beautiful family.
don't they?</b></font>

755
01:06:33.000 --> 01:06:37.483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah. that little one. April.
did you see her bring me pancakes?</b></font>

756
01:06:42.920 --> 01:06:44.524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We've gotta help them.</b></font>

757
01:06:45.000 --> 01:06:46.411
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know.</b></font>

758
01:06:47.600 --> 01:06:50.080
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I'll start with the Chevy.
- Heh.</b></font>

759
01:08:12.240 --> 01:08:13.526
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Carolyn!</b></font>

760
01:08:14.560 --> 01:08:15.607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you okay?</b></font>

761
01:08:15.760 --> 01:08:16.921
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Carolyn. open the door.</b></font>

762
01:08:17.080 --> 01:08:18.161
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Carolyn. open up!</b></font>

763
01:08:25.160 --> 01:08:26.207
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you okay?</b></font>

764
01:08:26.360 --> 01:08:27.646
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Oh. I'm fine.
- Are you sick?</b></font>

765
01:08:27.800 --> 01:08:30.644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I woke up feeling nauseous. that's all.
- I thought I saw...</b></font>

766
01:08:30.800 --> 01:08:33.041
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I hear Roger and the girls.</b></font>

767
01:08:33.200 --> 01:08:34.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One minute.</b></font>

768
01:08:46.520 --> 01:08:48.648
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Guys. do you wanna play a game?
- Boring!</b></font>

769
01:08:48.800 --> 01:08:49.926
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you. Daddy.</b></font>

770
01:08:51.200 --> 01:08:52.361
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's go inside.</b></font>

771
01:08:56.640 --> 01:08:57.801
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought that was you.</b></font>

772
01:08:58.000 --> 01:08:59.206
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. I hope you don't mind.</b></font>

773
01:08:59.400 --> 01:09:02.051
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I got a good deal on a rebuild
at that wrecking yard in Smithfield.</b></font>

774
01:09:02.240 --> 01:09:05.289
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- No. you look like you know what you're doing.
- Yeah. we'll see.</b></font>

775
01:09:08.240 --> 01:09:09.890
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Got a nice place here. Roger.</b></font>

776
01:09:10.080 --> 01:09:12.401
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine and I always wanted
a spot in the country.</b></font>

777
01:09:12.560 --> 01:09:13.891
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll sell you this one.</b></font>

778
01:09:16.080 --> 01:09:17.605
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. hand me a wrench. would you?</b></font>

779
01:09:20.240 --> 01:09:24.689
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. uh. it really means a lot
to us to have you here.</b></font>

780
01:09:24.840 --> 01:09:27.923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I gotta admit. I was a little
bit skeptical going in.</b></font>

781
01:09:29.120 --> 01:09:32.283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just wanna say thank you. though.
for coming out when you did.</b></font>

782
01:09:34.080 --> 01:09:37.687
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't take the credit.
That's. uh... That's all Lorraine.</b></font>

783
01:09:37.840 --> 01:09:40.605
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I didn't want to.
- Oh. Why's that?</b></font>

784
01:09:43.920 --> 01:09:47.322
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Whatever Lorraine sees. feels. touches.
it helps people.</b></font>

785
01:09:47.480 --> 01:09:49.608
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But it also takes a toll on her.</b></font>

786
01:09:49.840 --> 01:09:51.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Little piece each time.</b></font>

787
01:09:55.160 --> 01:09:57.891
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Couple months ago
we were working on a case.</b></font>

788
01:09:59.440 --> 01:10:01.169
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She saw something.</b></font>

789
01:10:11.680 --> 01:10:13.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It took a real big piece.</b></font>

790
01:10:15.120 --> 01:10:16.645
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When we got home...</b></font>

791
01:10:16.840 --> 01:10:19.844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...she went into our room.
locked herself in...</b></font>

792
01:10:20.000 --> 01:10:22.844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...didn't talk. didn't eat.
didn't come out for eight days.</b></font>

793
01:10:23.800 --> 01:10:25.131
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What'd she see?</b></font>

794
01:10:28.080 --> 01:10:29.320
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get out of here!</b></font>

795
01:10:30.400 --> 01:10:31.640
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

796
01:10:32.160 --> 01:10:33.810
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I won't ask.</b></font>

797
01:10:51.400 --> 01:10:54.563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I need to reload. You want some?</b></font>

798
01:10:55.040 --> 01:10:56.565
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm good. thanks.</b></font>

799
01:10:57.400 --> 01:10:58.686
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

800
01:11:43.400 --> 01:11:45.243
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Look what she made me do.</i></b></font>

801
01:12:28.920 --> 01:12:31.241
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Look what she made me do.</i></b></font>

802
01:12:34.080 --> 01:12:35.286
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Hey-</i></b></font>

803
01:12:42.720 --> 01:12:43.767
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed?</b></font>

804
01:12:43.960 --> 01:12:45.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look what she made me do!</b></font>

805
01:12:47.360 --> 01:12:48.964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed! Ed!</b></font>

806
01:12:49.600 --> 01:12:50.840
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed!</b></font>

807
01:12:51.960 --> 01:12:53.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dude. you okay?</b></font>

808
01:12:53.320 --> 01:12:54.810
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hold up. Brad. What's going on?</b></font>

809
01:12:54.960 --> 01:12:57.884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I saw someone. There was
a woman dressed as a maid.</b></font>

810
01:13:01.560 --> 01:13:03.528
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed? Ed. we're getting something.</b></font>

811
01:13:08.800 --> 01:13:11.644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- It's just Cindy. She's sleepwalking.
- No. wait. We need this.</b></font>

812
01:13:11.800 --> 01:13:13.370
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why do we need pictures of Cindy?</b></font>

813
01:13:14.320 --> 01:13:15.845
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She didn't trigger it.</b></font>

814
01:13:16.000 --> 01:13:19.322
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What do you mean she didn't trigger it?
- Somebody's with her.</b></font>

815
01:13:22.480 --> 01:13:23.641
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who?</b></font>

816
01:13:27.560 --> 01:13:28.925
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy!</b></font>

817
01:13:32.640 --> 01:13:33.926
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy!</b></font>

818
01:13:40.680 --> 01:13:42.091
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy!</b></font>

819
01:13:42.240 --> 01:13:43.890
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Hey. over here. It's safe.</i></b></font>

820
01:13:44.040 --> 01:13:45.929
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's someone else in there with her.</b></font>

821
01:13:47.200 --> 01:13:49.521
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm hearing another voice. Here. listen.</b></font>

822
01:13:54.320 --> 01:13:56.527
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Follow me. This way.</i></b></font>

823
01:13:58.000 --> 01:13:59.809
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>This is where I hide.</i></b></font>

824
01:14:04.960 --> 01:14:06.200
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy?</b></font>

825
01:14:08.720 --> 01:14:10.051
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cindy?</b></font>

826
01:14:11.880 --> 01:14:13.041
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where'd she go. Ed?</b></font>

827
01:14:13.440 --> 01:14:15.044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Windows are locked.</b></font>

828
01:14:18.080 --> 01:14:20.048
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed. where'd she go?</b></font>

829
01:14:21.560 --> 01:14:22.925
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Brad. get the UV light.</b></font>

830
01:14:23.080 --> 01:14:25.242
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- The what?
- Just ask Drew.</b></font>

831
01:14:26.360 --> 01:14:29.170
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I need a UV light.</b></font>

832
01:14:29.320 --> 01:14:30.845
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here. that's it. Go. go. go. go!</b></font>

833
01:14:37.400 --> 01:14:38.925
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Turn off the light.</b></font>

834
01:14:42.560 --> 01:14:44.130
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get out of the way.</b></font>

835
01:14:47.280 --> 01:14:48.406
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

836
01:15:17.680 --> 01:15:19.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hit the lights!</b></font>

837
01:15:31.280 --> 01:15:32.770
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Found her.</b></font>

838
01:15:34.400 --> 01:15:35.447
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here we go.</b></font>

839
01:15:36.040 --> 01:15:38.281
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- All right. You got her?
- Yeah.</b></font>

840
01:15:50.000 --> 01:15:53.049
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's where Rory hides
when he's afraid.</b></font>

841
01:16:18.840 --> 01:16:21.764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hon? Could I have April's
music box. please?</b></font>

842
01:16:24.840 --> 01:16:27.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- How's Cindy?
- She doesn't remember a thing.</b></font>

843
01:16:30.520 --> 01:16:31.851
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here you go.</b></font>

844
01:16:32.600 --> 01:16:33.886
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

845
01:17:11.520 --> 01:17:12.885
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine!</b></font>

846
01:17:16.960 --> 01:17:18.200
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

847
01:17:31.080 --> 01:17:32.320
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine!</b></font>

848
01:17:32.560 --> 01:17:33.800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine!</b></font>

849
01:17:38.160 --> 01:17:39.571
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine!</b></font>

850
01:17:40.360 --> 01:17:41.771
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine!</b></font>

851
01:18:32.920 --> 01:18:35.651
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She made me do it.</b></font>

852
01:18:36.720 --> 01:18:39.291
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She made me do it.</b></font>

853
01:19:00.960 --> 01:19:03.611
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She made me do it.</b></font>

854
01:19:47.320 --> 01:19:48.367
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed!</b></font>

855
01:19:48.560 --> 01:19:50.369
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on! Lorraine!</b></font>

856
01:19:58.200 --> 01:19:59.326
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed!</b></font>

857
01:20:00.200 --> 01:20:01.884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ed. I know what she did.</b></font>

858
01:20:02.080 --> 01:20:04.651
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- I got you. I know. It's okay.
- I know what she did.</b></font>

859
01:20:04.800 --> 01:20:07.724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know what she did. She possessed
the mother to kill the child.</b></font>

860
01:20:07.880 --> 01:20:09.405
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She visits Carolyn every night.</b></font>

861
01:20:09.560 --> 01:20:12.404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's what the bruise marks are!
She's feeding off of her!</b></font>

862
01:20:25.520 --> 01:20:27.090
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Uh...</b></font>

863
01:20:27.320 --> 01:20:28.765
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy?</b></font>

864
01:20:33.240 --> 01:20:34.480
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy!</b></font>

865
01:20:34.880 --> 01:20:36.166
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you okay?</b></font>

866
01:20:36.760 --> 01:20:38.091
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy!</b></font>

867
01:20:39.600 --> 01:20:40.647
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Grab her!</b></font>

868
01:20:43.160 --> 01:20:44.730
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daddy! Help!</b></font>

869
01:20:45.600 --> 01:20:46.681
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nancy!</b></font>

870
01:20:53.920 --> 01:20:55.001
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is she okay?</b></font>

871
01:20:55.200 --> 01:20:56.406
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's okay. I got you.</b></font>

872
01:20:56.560 --> 01:20:57.607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you get that?</b></font>

873
01:20:59.880 --> 01:21:01.086
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

874
01:21:04.240 --> 01:21:07.244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll have the footage developed
and get it over to Father Gordon.</b></font>

875
01:21:07.400 --> 01:21:11.405
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's our liaison at the church.
I imagine we'll get a pretty fast response.</b></font>

876
01:21:11.560 --> 01:21:13.608
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Listen. Roger?
- Yeah?</b></font>

877
01:21:13.800 --> 01:21:16.963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Listen. when we get the exorcist.
I'll be back. But Lorraine...</b></font>

878
01:21:17.120 --> 01:21:20.203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Yeah. I understand.
- Until then Drew's gonna keep an eye on you.</b></font>

879
01:21:20.360 --> 01:21:22.727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Hey. Ed. thank you for everything.
- Yeah.</b></font>

880
01:21:24.160 --> 01:21:25.446
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Mommy?</i></b></font>

881
01:21:27.760 --> 01:21:29.410
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's everything.</b></font>

882
01:21:41.320 --> 01:21:42.685
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Mommy?</i></b></font>

883
01:22:01.000 --> 01:22:02.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Judy?</b></font>

884
01:22:02.440 --> 01:22:03.805
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. God!</b></font>

885
01:22:03.960 --> 01:22:05.086
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Judy?</b></font>

886
01:22:13.760 --> 01:22:15.683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine! Wait!</b></font>

887
01:22:17.280 --> 01:22:18.805
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lorraine. What?</b></font>

888
01:22:18.960 --> 01:22:20.325
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mom. it's me. ls Judy okay?</b></font>

889
01:22:20.480 --> 01:22:22.960
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- What?
- Can you go check. please?</b></font>

890
01:22:23.520 --> 01:22:25.204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Damn it. Mom. just check. please!</b></font>

891
01:22:25.360 --> 01:22:28.204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Are you gonna tell me what's going on?
- It's Judy.</b></font>

892
01:22:28.360 --> 01:22:29.885
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What? What do you mean?</b></font>

893
01:22:30.880 --> 01:22:32.006
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

894
01:22:33.360 --> 01:22:35.522
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh. thank God.</b></font>

895
01:22:36.160 --> 01:22:39.369
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mom. I'm sorry. I didn't mean
to scare you. I'll explain later. okay?</b></font>

896
01:22:41.000 --> 01:22:42.331
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What the hell happened?</b></font>

