1075
01:43:18.400 --> 01:43:20.482
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'd take a guy with a gun any day.</b></font>

1076
01:43:24.680 --> 01:43:26.205
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You did good.</b></font>

1077
01:43:26.640 --> 01:43:28.051
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. you did.</b></font>

1078
01:44:28.680 --> 01:44:31.809
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll call Father Gordon
and let him know what happened.</b></font>

1079
01:44:32.720 --> 01:44:34.290
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sounds good.</b></font>

1080
01:44:59.520 --> 01:45:02.126
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The Vatican approved the exorcism.</b></font>

1081
01:45:02.440 --> 01:45:04.442
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Heh. Nice timing.</b></font>

1082
01:45:06.040 --> 01:45:09.726
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And if we can. then he'd like
to meet with us tomorrow.</b></font>

1083
01:45:09.880 --> 01:45:12.406
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's a case in Long Island
he'd like to discuss.</b></font>

1084
01:45:12.560 --> 01:45:13.641
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

